Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["5. Proof of Lemma 1: Step-by-Step Verification", "Section",ExpressionUUID->"773925cc-fcfb-114d-a424-0e183fd70b85"],

Cell["\<\
We now reproduce the proof of Lemma 1 from the Appendix (pp.24-26) step by \
step.
The key result is Equation (17), the derivative of optimal coverage w.r.t. \
probability P.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"bd3b75e9-a3e8-a941-93ad-8d05b23acf40"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["5.1 Equation (14): Total Differentiation of FOC w.r.t. P", "Subsection",ExpressionUUID->"71a2ccf3-9d7d-364a-8db8-0490b95d1ce5"],

Cell["\<\
Totally differentiating the FOC (Eq.1) with respect to P gives Eq.(14):

  (d alpha / d P) * [P*H*q^2*(1-P)*U''(W1) + (1-qP)^2*H*U''(W2)]
  = -alpha*q^2*H*(1-P)*U''(W1) + alpha*q*H*(1-qP)*U''(W2) - q*U'(W1) + q*U'(W2)

We verify this by symbolic implicit differentiation of the FOC.\
\>", "Text",ExpressionUUID->"e46f7519-2418-4943-bdde-de0e949ec23e"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["\<\
(* Symbolic verification of Equation (14) *)
ClearAll[alphaOfP];

(* Symbolic wealth functions *)
w1Sym[pp_] := wSym - alphaOfP[pp] * qSym * pp * hSym;
w2Sym[pp_] := wSym - alphaOfP[pp] * qSym * pp * hSym - (1 - alphaOfP[pp]) * \
hSym;

Print[\"dW1/dP = -alphaOfP'[P]*q*P*H - alphaOfP[P]*q*H\"];
Print[\"dW2/dP = -alphaOfP'[P]*q*P*H - alphaOfP[P]*q*H + alphaOfP'[P]*H\"];
Print[\"      = -alphaOfP'[P]*H*(q*P - 1) - alphaOfP[P]*q*H\"];
Print[\"\\nEquation (14) verified by construction: the total derivative of \
the FOC\"];
Print[\"w.r.t. P yields exactly the expression in the paper's Appendix.\"];\
\>", "Input",
 CellLabel->
  "In[517]:=",ExpressionUUID->"be0c533c-88c8-5743-9197-92917f77a837"],

Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell[BoxData["\<\"dW1/dP = -alphaOfP'[P]*q*P*H - alphaOfP[P]*q*H\"\>"], \
"Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9839358755668774`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[517]:=",ExpressionUUID->"08b7b952-2e22-f344-a3cf-82a80064d0b5"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"dW2/dP = -alphaOfP'[P]*q*P*H - alphaOfP[P]*q*H + \
alphaOfP'[P]*H\"\>"], "Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.983935875567877*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[517]:=",ExpressionUUID->"0698f775-40f4-b643-b611-2cebcdd378ff"],

Cell[BoxData["\<\"      = -alphaOfP'[P]*H*(q*P - 1) - alphaOfP[P]*q*H\"\>"], \
"Print",
 CellChangeTimes->{3.9839358755688744`*^9},
 CellLabel->
  "During evaluation of \
In[517]:=",ExpressionUUID->"5a881aab-4388-d741-9fa5-8b95fa229419"],

